{"tid":2423373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平：中共帶領廣大衣民“打土豪、分田地”   爲擺脫貧困創造了根本政治條件","createTime":"2021-02-26T01:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T07:03:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6f7b2b498f0cc0b1a55ccf672e42a9f49daaa444","tid":2423373,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T01:14:13.000Z","msg":"習近平稱，中共十八大以來，平均每年有1000多萬人脫貧，相當於一個中等國家的人口脫貧。現行標準下9899萬農村貧困人口全部脫貧，832個貧困縣全部摘帽，12.8萬個貧困村全部出列，區域性整體貧困得到解決，完成了消除絕對貧困的艱鉅任務。<br />\n<br />\n習近平宣稱，中共在脫貧上取得全面勝利，創造了所謂&ldquo;彪炳史冊的人間奇蹟&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n值得關注的是，習近平還讚揚中共當年&ldquo;打土豪、分田地&rdquo;，聲稱中共帶領廣大農民&ldquo;打土豪、分田地&rdquo;，實行&ldquo;耕者有其田&rdquo;，幫助窮苦人翻身，建立了中共政權，爲擺脫貧困創造了根本政治條件。<br />\n<br />\n外媒報導，習近平是第一個公開表揚&ldquo;打土豪分田地&rdquo;這段黑歷史的中共領導人。<br />\n<br />\n《新唐人》報導指出，中共當年的&ldquo;打土豪分田地&rdquo;，就是直接搶掠鄉紳的土地和財富。而習近平稱讚&ldquo;打土豪分田地&rdquo;被認爲可能要對有錢人下手，不僅僅限於搶劫民企。<br />\n<br />\n近年來，中國民營企業家不斷出事，富豪榜也被網民稱爲&ldquo;殺豬榜&rdquo;，但作爲隱形鉅富的中共高層權貴家族從來不上榜。網上不斷傳出暗示有錢人快走的消息。<br />\n<br />\n北京普華商學院創始人崔山鷹2018年的一段演講視頻早前在網上曝光。他透露：北京十幾個擁有上百億資產的富豪，被北京市公安局和安全局下令禁止出京。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.soundofhope.org/post/478397?lang=b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundofhope.org%2Fpost%2F478397%3Flang%3Db5&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6xSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=7c89b6dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundofhope.org/post/478397?lang=b5</a>"},{"pid":"eedcc1883608c9ef55f30429f4be70ed2f01d210","tid":2423373,"uid":263534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T01:16:44.000Z","msg":"養到你咁肥就係等呢日劏啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012afbae0a79aa4ec0e3766a9fcdcbf4cbe82d80","tid":2423373,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T01:46:45.000Z","msg":"無產階級全面脫貧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa2c63b7f2938e978c1cfbc2dff0dc436c32770","tid":2423373,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:02:17.000Z","msg":"習近平捐咗香港冇人住d屋同樓未？"},{"pid":"86ce2fc012bafbd0cb62ecbed551492ec1d08350","tid":2423373,"uid":18772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:06:02.000Z","msg":"共產分裂中國 排除異己<br />\n非黨員即不是代表中國  無權無勢<br />\n方式如同將非黨員睇成少數民族<br />\n只論多寡"},{"pid":"0b54fae384f5f67c47381d46fcebddf92c018ebe","tid":2423373,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:23:24.000Z","msg":"習近平還讚揚中共當年&ldquo;打土豪、分田地&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n遲下到香港.<br />\n有錢有地當然走,<br />\n無錢無地等分地."},{"pid":"d525fc707b646840a54cd4116a9f3817e6601103","tid":2423373,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6660a26a5225508cdc526dc8e4604a5fe6d4efd4","tid":2423373,"uid":301820,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:39:14.000Z","msg":"如果當年土豪、地主咁撚衰<br />\n洗撚共產黨打咩，一早被軍閥打擊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿爺講太公地主係個好人<br />\n軍閥之亂唔洗農民交租<br />\n仲資助過共匪<br />\n最後被人鬥死咗<br />\n村民淨係保得住阿爺<br />\n<br />\n妓女都比共產黨有誠信<br />\n因為比畜牲好少少，佢哋識著衫"},{"pid":"18b5cb9adade034545214e4d58cd0e500c009d21","tid":2423373,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:41:45.000Z","msg":"香港要學喇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e923f2afd1abd4047002e62bdbc9181a7b45a27","tid":2423373,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:44:06.000Z","msg":"條友想連任做緊勢, 佢係香港鉗得咁緊因為第二任內無乜建樹, 唔夠政治籌碼俾佢打破中共慣例連任第三次<br />\n<br />\n如果香港又亂過俾外國制口加大制裁, 加上拜登上左場但係貿易戰條款一條都無撤到, 打印度又死一大堆人, 任內又爆武肺, 而家得返所謂攻堅脫貧可以鳩吹<br />\n<br />\n江澤民馬雲李嘉誠呢d舊派系既全部走左資去外國, 以前香港就係呢班人既集資遊樂場來, 2019年頭中聯辦換左人就係為左呢單野"},{"pid":"d75cfedd7c721c40f8a0cb6c9193ea50515959e8","tid":2423373,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b54fae384f5f67c47381d46fcebddf92c018ebe","tid":2423373,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:23:24.000Z","msg":"習近平還讚揚中共當年&ldquo;打土豪、分田地&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n遲下到香港.<br />\n有錢有地當然走,<br />\n無錢無地等分地."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:46:44.000Z","msg":"係就好啦，唔好得個講字<br />\n<br />\n打土豪、分田地"},{"pid":"4c5470ea389288753b10b24e7da81c82624996f8","tid":2423373,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18b5cb9adade034545214e4d58cd0e500c009d21","tid":2423373,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:41:45.000Z","msg":"香港要學喇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:47:08.000Z","msg":"打土豪、分土地"},{"pid":"32c7c21c56b0df1d35fb9cba74447feb06f1d9c6","tid":2423373,"uid":225347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3nwCaO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3nwCaO.gif&h=ad4e894c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a806041a2de2aca156623de4c5f5d1c79a1f95f","tid":2423373,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:28:43.000Z","msg":"習仔幾時同農民工共產<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e987b44da9a3e22302b93fba54d5dbe0040d4d","tid":2423373,"uid":68780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:29:33.000Z","msg":"支那農民唔係冇土地權咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbaa6eaaabe66509642e97776f3068ba3828a3a0","tid":2423373,"uid":45353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":